{{Top|leg}}
The '''dlock plant''' was a tall, leafy plant with large, blue leaves. The leaves were said to have been the most fragrant and soothing of all the plants in the [[Endor/Legends|Endorian]] forest.

On one [[Halloween/Legends|Hallowe'en]], [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket Wystri Warrick]] and other [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] used dlock leaves to calm a [[hanadak]] and lead it away from [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]].

